{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"45ab00a58c","title":"先打丁德隆后打周祥初孔令愉","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"3858cb7034","index":0,"year":1936,"month":11,"day":19,"articleId":"45ab00a58c"}],"tags":[{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji9-2","name":"毛泽东全集第9卷(2)","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives8/main/mao-quanji/maoquanji9-2.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji9-2":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"7aeb8ea5e7","type":"paragraph","text":"先打丁德隆后打周祥初孔令愉！","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji9-2","articleId":"45ab00a58c"},{"id":"d5649a006f","type":"paragraph","text":"（1936年11月19日）彭：","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji9-2","articleId":"45ab00a58c"},{"id":"34b574db83","type":"paragraph","text":"我军先打其右路丁师。对周孔似宜让其北进数十里，然后坚决拒阻之，以便我军消灭了师后，向其周孔之侧后打去。又二方面军主力宜跟进为预备队，其一部则坚决拒阻王军。如何，请依情况决定。","index":2,"publicationId":"maoquanji9-2","articleId":"45ab00a58c"},{"id":"1811912ba3","type":"paragraph","text":"毛","index":3,"publicationId":"maoquanji9-2","articleId":"45ab00a58c"},{"id":"3f06af1e1e","type":"paragraph","text":"十九日","index":4,"publicationId":"maoquanji9-2","articleId":"45ab00a58c"},{"id":"403f60edb6","type":"paragraph","text":"[1]这是毛泽东给红军前敌总指挥兼政治委员、第一方面军司令员彭德怀的电报。","index":5,"publicationId":"maoquanji9-2","articleId":"45ab00a58c"},{"id":"89fd6c48d3","type":"paragraph","text":"[2]丁师，指国民党军西北“汇”总司令部第一路第二纵队第七十八师，师长丁德隆。","index":6,"publicationId":"maoquanji9-2","articleId":"45ab00a58c"},{"id":"30b953d372","type":"paragraph","text":"[3]周孔，指周祥初、孔令恂，当时分别任国民党军西北“”总司令部第一路第二纵队第四十三师师长和第九十七师师长。","index":7,"publicationId":"maoquanji9-2","articleId":"45ab00a58c"},{"id":"2767acd28e","type":"paragraph","text":"14]王军，指国民党军西北“剩”总司令部第一路第六纵队司令王以暂指挥的东北军一部。","index":8,"publicationId":"maoquanji9-2","articleId":"45ab00a58c"}],"page":{"id":"925d3e25a8","publicationId":"maoquanji9-2","articleId":"45ab00a58c","start":5,"end":5}}}},"__N_SSG":true}